      <title>阳光、海洋和出口让南欧有理由沾沾自喜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/europe-rebound-latest-sun-sea-exports-give-spain-greece-reason-to-be-smug</link>
      <description><![CDATA[长期被富裕的北方邻国嘲笑的南欧经济体在巩固其作为欧元区增长驱动力的角色时已经扭转了局面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/europe-rebound-latest-sun-sea-exports-give-spain-greece-reason-to-be-smug</guid>
