    <item>
      <title>奥夫拉多尔称厄瓜多尔前副总统格拉斯被从驻基多大使馆带走</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/amlo-says-former-ecuador-vp-glas-taken-from-embassy-in-quito</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥总统安德烈斯·曼努埃尔·洛佩斯·奥夫拉多尔表示，厄瓜多尔警方闯入墨西哥位于首都基多的大使馆，厄瓜多尔前副总统豪尔赫·格拉斯一直在那里庇护并拘留了他。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/amlo-says-former-ecuador-vp-glas-taken-from-embassy-in-quito</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 04:49:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚称以色列尚未就车队袭击提供足够细节</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/australia-says-israel-yet-to-give-enough-detail-on-convoy-strike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚正在寻求有关以色列致命导弹袭击的更多信息，该袭击造成一名澳大利亚公民死亡，政府准备任命一名特别顾问，负责跟踪这场悲剧的调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/australia-says-israel-yet-to-give-enough-detail-on-convoy-strike</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 03:39:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国及其盟国将于4月7日在菲律宾举行海上演习</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/us-allies-to-conduct-maritime-drills-in-philippines-on-april-7</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于马尼拉和北京在争议海域的紧张局势加剧，美国、澳大利亚、日本和菲律宾将于 4 月 7 日在南海举行联合军事演习。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/us-allies-to-conduct-maritime-drills-in-philippines-on-april-7</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 03:02:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国政党承诺使用美国比特币 ETF 来争夺选票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/south-korean-party-pledges-access-to-us-bitcoin-etfs-in-race-for-votes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国议会选举的竞选活动凸显了该国作为世界上最大的加密货币市场之一的地位，两个主要政党都在宣传相关的激励措施来赢得选票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/south-korean-party-pledges-access-to-us-bitcoin-etfs-in-race-for-votes</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>秘鲁领导人称劳力士是“借来的”，手链不是卡地亚</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/peru-leader-says-rolexes-were-a-loan-bracelet-wasn-t-cartier</link>
      <description><![CDATA[陷入困境的秘鲁总统迪娜·博卢阿特(Dina Boluarte)对一套豪华手表和其他珠宝的起源有了不同的看法，这进一步削弱了这位世界上最不受欢迎的领导人之一的声誉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/peru-leader-says-rolexes-were-a-loan-bracelet-wasn-t-cartier</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 22:40:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登将在威斯康星州大学城推广学生贷款“B 计划”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/student-loan-forgiveness-alternate-plan-to-be-pitched-by-biden-in-madison</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据白宫官员称，总统乔·拜登计划周一在威斯康星州麦迪逊市宣传其政府的替代性广泛学生债务减免计划。这座城市是 2024 年战场州数千名大学生的家园。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/student-loan-forgiveness-alternate-plan-to-be-pitched-by-biden-in-madison</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 22:38:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国证券交易委员会 (SEC) 在新型“影子”内幕交易打击中赢得审判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/sec-wins-novel-shadow-insider-trading-trial-against-executive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国证券交易委员会在其开创性的内幕交易案件中赢得了陪审团的裁决，该案件旨在禁止员工利用有关自己公司的非公开信息来押注竞争对手的股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/sec-wins-novel-shadow-insider-trading-trial-against-executive</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 22:04:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗要求美国靠边站，准备对以色列做出回应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/iran-tells-us-to-step-aside-as-it-readies-response-to-israel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗表示，在该国准备对以色列驻叙利亚领事馆涉嫌袭击事件做出回应之际，它要求美国“靠边站”，而其在中东的主要代理人真主党则警告这个犹太国家，它已做好战争准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/iran-tells-us-to-step-aside-as-it-readies-response-to-israel</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 16:02:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
